author: Philippine Statistics Authority
maintainer: Philippine Statistics Authority, Office of the National Statistician
name: dealers-prices-
notes: This dataset contains the dealers' prices of fertilizers and pesticides.

resources.description: This dataset contains the dealers' price of pesticide in solid form by farm cheminal, by region and by province. This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from 2000 to the latest available month/year.
resources.name: Pesticide (Solid): Dealers' Prices by Region and by Province

resources.description: This dataset contains the dealers' price of pesticide in liquid form by farm cheminal, by region and by province. This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from 2000 to the latest available month/year.
resources.name: Pesticide (Liquid): Dealers' Prices by Region and by Province

resources.description: This dataset contains the dealers' prices of fertilizers by grade by region and by Province.  This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from  1990 to the latest available month/year.
resources.name: Fertilizers: Dealers' Prices by Region and by Province

title: Dealers' Prices
